Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just feel that cool breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's going to be good, I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm drawing pictures\Nfor a game makers club...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F..F..Fujikawa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean \Nto scare you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late if you don't get a move on.\NWhat've you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love coming to the \Nriverbank to relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty easygoing for someone\Nwho just started classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What about your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Murakami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to pretend I didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess they aren't going to\Nkeep talking forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have your\Nheadphones today Fujikawa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but I try not to listen to music\Non the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of sounds out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of input for a sound person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figure maybe it's good inspiration\Nfor my song making?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one listening to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't exactly seem like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... It just feels like people are laughing at me\Nwhenever I'm in a crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I cover my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make another song, Fujikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to get it down yesterday\Nsince I've got my part-time job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... what kind of job?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a waitress at a family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something, Fujikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make music and you're a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my first name, Honda-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel better if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay, then... Kayo-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can call you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what communicating gets you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the whole SNS Club is all together\Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Early and in sync!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whole"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It is just the \Nfour of us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were pretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only first year we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm so sorry! I didn't \Nmean it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it. We might get \Nsome new people in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the four of us \Nhave to work hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sweet positivity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. How about we have \Nlunch together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you already promise\Nsomeone else you would, Honda-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... no, I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's that. Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsukeyou make my day
