Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonnan ja hottarakashi de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonnan ja hottokenakute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iesu or noo ha itsumo kakureteru
