Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijoubu tte omoeta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akkenai kurai de okashikatta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna wakuwaku o oikaketeru kimochi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou made no jibun no souzou o koete yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konnichiwa make my day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minna ga motteru mahou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshou de ichiban no nani ka ga mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deaeru yo make my day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bukiyou de arigatou watashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuki dake ga tsureteku sekai ga matteru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fun Production
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having lunch with my upperclassmen\Nin the club room today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Are you going to show off your pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! I'm keeping them a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't draw yesterday... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing quite like an old friend running away\Nclutching something she's shy about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get embarrassed just thinking about\Nother people seeing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, all I've ever done is copying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work out, it doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'm up for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who frolic so harmoniously through the wen,\Nmake my garden complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold the evening's dew upon the leontochir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were having so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H..Honda-san! Just wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't write a scenario that resonates with people\Nif you don't speak the lines out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just wrote some really good ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it an explosion of catharsis, or...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget I said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sketchbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it! Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay, but just the first few pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've been copying our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of weird seeing someone else\Ndraw artwork from our game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm going to start... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with these myself,\Nso they're kind of all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that horse is already out of the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus I didn't get enough \Non the way to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'd you think of our game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at first it really threw me for a loop since the art was so different from
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the manga I usually read...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I started to get into it,\Nand that made drawing it super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about how good it looks\Nas long as you're drawing with feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of raw art I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're even!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you show me what \Nyou wrote, Seki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still writing this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you when it's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want to see one of your old ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My old ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like from when I was in Writing Club...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nay, no, not in a million years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stardust Desires
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:20.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stardust Desires, Act 1. By Iris."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stardust Desires\NAct 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stardust Desires\NAct 1\NBy Iris
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It was then, on the eve \Nof my 3,037th birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sky full a'sparkle with stars that did not\Nso much shine as weep from the heavens-"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shii!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reciting! You'd better \Nforget every single line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? When did you get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't want to spoil the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well try speaking up next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What say we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:44.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Dewdrop\NTea\NOolong\NTea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know, Honda-chan, Stardust Desires\Nis among Lady Seki's finest works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's got some serious twists,\Nstarting with how the heroine-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lunch tastes like lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm complimenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister is super \Nexcited for the next act!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go spreading it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we please stop talking about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about how \NI pressured you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to \Nseeing your artwork, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well for our next phase, how about we really put\Nsome work into Samü and Stella's love scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might pop on screen, but personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samü...\NI think we need a story that really draws people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was that really cool boy from the game.\NI think we need a story that really draws people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was that really cool boy from the game.\NLike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was that really cool boy from the game.\NHmm... Like maybe they buy a house out in Tochigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I drew him...\NHmm... Like maybe they buy a house out in Tochigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Like maybe they buy \Na house out in Tochigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Original\NGood luck in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be all for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, Fujikawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit looks super good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how many are in your party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, since we're making\Na side-story this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're not going to have to worry\Nabout the character design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just use what Teru-senpai\Nalready made for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the senior who started this club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very same, although she's in college now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did the cutest artwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was a real beaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gathered the three of us out of the blue\Nand told us we should make a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... And you remember when\Nshe cosplayed as a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A potato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to change the \Ndesigns if you want, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge of the artwork, so be sure\Nto let us know if you have any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the art was so cute, plus the characters\Nand the story were so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, the characters were \Nall so pretty and so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like something out of a shoujo manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe there's \Nsome room for an older man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well let's get all our ideas \Nout in the open for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once we're done with that,\Nwe can work on a plot that'll get the story going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what you were writing\Nthis afternoon in the club room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to think of \Nsome standout lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standout?! That's what you did before, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't manage your time properly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you ended up holed up in that room\Nwith Teru-senpai right before Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! It'll be fine this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This time"? You started writing Stardust Desires
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in\Njunior high and still haven't written the second act.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please stop talking about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a courtesy to our other customers, please hold\Nyour meeting at a reasonable volume. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sorry, Fujikawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now back to the subject at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.71,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Plot          I'm going to write\Nthe heck out of it! \NAssignments from the Leader\NMe\NWrite the script\N(Easy! About 300 kb?)                  Shii\NProgramming!\N(How much time to           Honda-san!\Nmake a website?)               Artwork\NCharacter design\NWe can use old stuff\NLayout design
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're done with the plot we can\Nturn things over to Honda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Script debugging\NFujikawa-san\NMusic, SFX\NRoyalty-free stuff works
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well this time do it \Nsooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't need to do the art yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya will need to decide what kind of artwork\Nshe'll need for the scenario first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I guess that's where we are for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any questions, Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's just, both of you seem like\Nyou get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's really important to be close\Nwhen you're working on a group project...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Close"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known Shiina since way back, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that? It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be pretty cute if you\Ndressed in all black like you used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I remember how you used \Nto talk just like a ma-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you have to pick\Nat every little thing all the time-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe she gave us the boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we made her mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, she's just serious about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shii has to get herself to cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of vim and vigor, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like she said, we didn't have enough time\Non our last project because I messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it looks like I've got to \Nwrite my heart out this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've got stacks of material,\Nand I'll need to use all my energy to-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll make some of the \Ncharacters older guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that... Er, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all just look so in sync, I don't know if I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best pick to help you make your next project...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I don't want you feeling \Nlike a third wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already finished that project, and now\Nwe want something that's all you, Honda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! And I'm serious about\Nwanting to see your drawings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's knock this out of the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really think we should put\Nsome older men in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh... I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they don't need the art yet,\Nbut maybe it's okay if I start now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself I'd get more serious,\Nso now I need to actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ayame's notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Idea Space
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a notebook\Nat the restaurant yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That someone forgot? Can't say I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't found it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My secret notebook, second \Nonly to mine own life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if you'd put things \Nback where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've gotten mixed up in my things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Idea Space
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I had no idea you wrote such...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, mature stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those're old scripts! You've \Ngot it all wrong, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact I didn't even write those!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she going on about?\NIn fact I didn't even write those!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for asking \Nyou to do this, Yumine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I've been wanting to\Ncheck out your club, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all I have to do is \Nshow them this sketchbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I feel too shy to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't make the game \Nunless they see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you show them yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-b-because I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had an upperclassman\Ndoing the art before, and it was so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I try to draw,\Nit all looks like my manga at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might get mad at me\Nfor being a bad replacement...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her house was always full \Nof those old manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but hard-boiled characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've \Nseen a drawing from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, leave it 'til you're in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And try not to look too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure it's possible to \Nlook too hard at a picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing keeping me calm\Nis thinking about my daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the fourth Saturday of the month!\NHe's coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those faces... that is \Nsome serious eye candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:11.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Make doujin games!\NSlack-eyed\NNight-owl\NShuttle-runners
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slack-eyed Night-owl Shuttle-runners..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Tama-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandma's been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretending I'm on the porch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She pretty much had her\Nhead in the clouds up until junior high...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's started making all sorts of faces\Nsince she found this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you found \Na nice club, Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse m-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us for the dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't expecting a guest so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive our carelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got snacks if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving one's body works \Nto stimulate the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club does make things,\Nand we have finished a project...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do hope you won't go around\Nspreading bad rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really not why I came...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to our club PR event, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here about Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. She asked me to do her a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted me to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wanted to see what \Nkind of club she was in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her! It's just our sound director\Nstressing over a melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look sharp, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well this is Tama-chan's first club ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's really serious\Nabout doing the best she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well she's definitely got \Nthat can-do attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to change, and I want to do\Neverything I can to support her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a little worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very worried, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's kind of ditzy,\Nbut is she getting along with the club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you use some frigging headphones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an expert or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought those tracings\Nof Honda-san's were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are are the only things\Nshe showed us, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she was just saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to show it to them\Nwhile I'm not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get embarrassed when people\Nlook at my drawings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't make anything \Nunless I show them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every embarrassing bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make her draw\Nanything embarrassing, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making her do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going through your head right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean to say is Tama-chan\Nhas to learn how to do digital art
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she's going to make the \Nartwork for the game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And do you have someone to teach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose Teru-senpai might \Nbe able to if we ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! We said we wouldn't\Nbother her anymore after she graduated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fujikawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you could talk to someone for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening? Maybe you \Ncould talk to Temawari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temawari...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean THE Temawari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The artist who did "800 Devilish and\NDelightful Shogi"? She's super famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't know she released a book like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Temawari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on the internet knows her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she has regular meetups\Nwith this one over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please introduce me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared the crap out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me \Nwe had a visitor?! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that NOW?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a friend of Honda-chan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kayo Fujikawa, the sound director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yumine Fuda. I'm a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know is why you can't pay attention\Nto what's going on while you're making music?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was making songs for a boy's love CD\NTemawari-san is making
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm having a pretty rough time with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great Temawari's making boy's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The illustrations are super nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if you're looking for someone to\Nhelp her do digital art, I think I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can think it over\Nonce we take a look at her drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they'd be hard-boiled types...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like she went all in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... That's mean! You don't have to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would Tama-chan think if she heard you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think she has a \Nthing to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be worried because her style's\Nso different from Teru-senpai's,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's really good!\NAnd it looks like she had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fun"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had her sketch something at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made such a nice face...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing with a face like that,\NI figured that our characters would look all happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And instead we get these manly men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend all you want, you're not fooling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. She's always been like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-welcome back, Yumine.\NDid you show them my sketchbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I just say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying something about how nice she looked\Ndrawing doesn't quite get the point across...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said, "Work hard.\NYou've still got a long way to go..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said you're fine as long as you\Nlook happy while you draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the characters are probably happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I look happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really think you \Nshould show them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who drew \Nthe pictures, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so that's what we're going for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world of art is ever expanding. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? What's the point of doing it\Nif we don't have you draw something fresh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Now I need to make \Nsure the scenario fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can help you with the digital stuff\Nif you're okay with it, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought you were busy\Nwith the Illustration Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you can help me \Nwhen I need help drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not thinking of how adorably\Nembarrassed you'd look drawing boy's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To-do-i-te i-ma-su ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akogare shisen tsumasaki senobi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fu-ra-ra na-ga-sa-re
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muchuu no umi o oyogu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurabii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should run away from here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just focusing on finishing up one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:36.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Broker Items
